name: Pina Bausch
description:
The titular track from CT Twenty's second release, 'Pina Bausch'.

Heavy, distorted bass lines and tearing synthwave arpeggios, perfectly punctuated with cynical, unashamed lyrics; all accompanied with a mixture of broken beats and four the floor percussive elements that will, undoubtedly, get you moving.

BeatsPerMinute.com: "The track is an incendiary juggernaut of electro beats and quick fire lyrical bars that gets more frenzied and frantic with each verse."

BrutalResonance.com: "...CT Twenty comes in with their UK-accented rhymes; soft words with fast paced lyrics, I was once again enamored with their work."
